Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:09.48,3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(838,444)}马尾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:09.48,2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(795,248)}教师点评
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:09.48,3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(677,731)}最后一条感觉挺微妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:09.48,2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\fs42\3c&H000000&\pos(618,251)\c&H70BCFE&}岛田美波的答案
